snippet.textDisplay:
Sanam Marvi, Saen Zahoor.. When such powerful voices come to Coke Studio, they neglect the need for backend vocals. This was and is the level of pure Coke Studio. This is the only song which I can listen to next 6 months from Coke Studio season 9. This is real coke studio. No doubt rock / pop etc., have their own tastes. But real essence for starting the coke studio to promote local cultural music to produce to blend with Sufism. 
And for Sanam Marvi, what a fab voice she has, if you really do understand music then you must be knowing that how beautifully she delivers such high and low notes.  Hats of for this combination.
